channel.title: Help with HybridScape
channel.description:
i downloaded moparscape and i was messing with the hybridscape folder(source) for a while and i want to know how i can get other people to play on it.
(also i downloaded testscape and i messed witht that but once i hit runserver it comes up in a black box and says starting tesetscape on 0.0.0.0:43594 someone tell me how to get that to work also)
TY

item.title: Help with HybridScape
item.dc:creator: @Simply_Z3R0 Simply Z3R0
item.description:
@Simply_Z3R0 wrote:

When it says starting testscape thing that means the server is turned on…

You can either do port forwarding or download hamachi, create a network (easy)
then tell people the Hamachi IP at the top of the Hamachi window and people can connect to your server by connecting to your network and using that IP…
